1
00:00:15,279 --> 00:00:15,980
Decree:

2
00:00:16,780 --> 00:00:17,760
Xie Lingfeng

3
00:00:18,179 --> 00:00:19,980
will take over as regent.

4
00:00:21,820 --> 00:00:23,539
He's my son after all.

5
00:00:24,859 --> 00:00:26,199
Even if we're estranged now,

6
00:00:27,379 --> 00:00:27,980
he'll

7
00:00:29,460 --> 00:00:31,260
be of use to me later.

8
00:00:31,960 --> 00:00:33,020
Yes, Your Highness.

9
00:00:54,219 --> 00:00:54,740
Lingfeng,

10
00:00:55,179 --> 00:00:56,020
what are you doing?

11
00:00:56,719 --> 00:00:58,340
Luo Yao has accepted your terms

12
00:00:58,460 --> 00:00:59,020
and is about to leave.

13
00:00:59,179 --> 00:01:00,560
Why do you want to kill her?

14
00:01:01,119 --> 00:01:03,119
She knows too many secrets.

15
00:01:03,679 --> 00:01:04,840
If one day she changes her mind,

16
00:01:05,219 --> 00:01:06,420
I will have no way out.

17
00:01:06,900 --> 00:01:08,319
That's why I can't let her go.

18
00:01:08,900 --> 00:01:10,459
I'm not a bloodthirsty person.

19
00:01:11,319 --> 00:01:12,379
Xie Lingfeng,

20
00:01:12,780 --> 00:01:14,000
how dare you!

21
00:01:23,060 --> 00:01:23,780
Lingfeng,

22
00:01:24,959 --> 00:01:26,680
I am your mother.

23
00:01:27,659 --> 00:01:28,980
Everything I did

24
00:01:29,379 --> 00:01:31,040
was to protect you.

25
00:01:31,560 --> 00:01:32,400
For me?

26
00:01:33,340 --> 00:01:34,040
Eight years ago,

27
00:01:34,120 --> 00:01:35,900
you were afraid of my identity being discovered,

28
00:01:36,200 --> 00:01:37,239
so you sent assassins

29
00:01:37,319 --> 00:01:38,659
to kill me

30
00:01:38,739 --> 00:01:39,579
and the monks in the temple.

31
00:01:40,019 --> 00:01:41,219
Is this for me?

32
00:01:42,500 --> 00:01:43,219
It's not like that.

33
00:01:44,299 --> 00:01:45,260
It's not like that.

34
00:01:45,560 --> 00:01:47,359
You gave me life,

35
00:01:48,400 --> 00:01:50,379
but you never raised me.

36
00:01:51,079 --> 00:01:52,700
And now you've killed my beloved.

37
00:01:53,540 --> 00:01:55,019
Today, I'll use your life

38
00:01:55,900 --> 00:01:58,480
to honor Luo Yao's spirit.

39
00:02:00,939 --> 00:02:01,420
Feng.

40
00:02:19,599 --> 00:02:21,039
♪If we face the same snowstorm one day♪

41
00:02:30,900 --> 00:02:31,580
Feng.

42
00:02:33,340 --> 00:02:34,360
You can't kill me.

43
00:02:35,340 --> 00:02:36,580
How will you explain

44
00:02:37,460 --> 00:02:39,180
to the world for killing your mother?

45
00:02:40,060 --> 00:02:41,719
The world will despise you.

46
00:02:41,780 --> 00:02:43,039
What the world thinks

47
00:02:43,120 --> 00:02:43,919
doesn't concern me.

48
00:02:45,300 --> 00:02:46,379
The one I cared about most

49
00:02:46,639 --> 00:02:48,000
is dead.

50
00:02:50,099 --> 00:02:53,240
Now I just want you to go to hell.

51
00:02:57,439 --> 00:02:58,020
Stop!

52
00:03:01,620 --> 00:03:03,000
You treacherous wretch,

53
00:03:13,560 --> 00:03:14,599
death would be

54
00:03:14,659 --> 00:03:15,900
too kind for you.

55
00:03:19,080 --> 00:03:19,620
I want you

56
00:03:19,699 --> 00:03:22,080
to spend your days in a monastery,

57
00:03:23,900 --> 00:03:25,639
confessing your sins,

58
00:03:26,659 --> 00:03:28,400
and never find peace!

59
00:03:45,159 --> 00:03:46,300
[Prince of Lin'an was assassinated.]

60
00:03:46,900 --> 00:03:49,259
[His son Xie Lingfeng succeeded him,]

61
00:03:49,560 --> 00:03:51,300
[and assisted the young emperor.]

62
00:03:51,740 --> 00:03:52,479
[The emperor issued a decree]

63
00:03:52,599 --> 00:03:54,199
[to investigate the case from eight years ago,]

64
00:03:54,599 --> 00:03:56,139
[which revealed the royal family's secrets.]

65
00:03:56,479 --> 00:03:57,319
[The Queen Mother,]

66
00:03:57,460 --> 00:03:58,840
[under the guise of the Hundred Treasures Office,]

67
00:03:58,979 --> 00:04:00,240
[amassed wealth and killed her own son,]

68
00:04:00,500 --> 00:04:02,699
[causing the wrongful death of Su Heng and the Xie Family Army.]

69
00:04:03,199 --> 00:04:04,340
[The Emperor was furious,]

70
00:04:04,900 --> 00:04:07,099
[posthumously granting them the title of general.]

71
00:04:07,659 --> 00:04:09,080
[The Queen Mother's reputation was tarnished,]

72
00:04:09,400 --> 00:04:10,419
[and she issued a decree of self-criticism,]

73
00:04:10,759 --> 00:04:12,939
[spending the rest of her life in the Jade Buddha Temple,]

74
00:04:13,419 --> 00:04:14,659
[never to return to the palace.]

75
00:04:28,639 --> 00:04:29,220
Brother,

76
00:04:30,279 --> 00:04:31,040
please take a look.

77
00:04:36,959 --> 00:04:38,100
Your Majesty is still afraid of me.

78
00:04:42,759 --> 00:04:43,459
Over the years,

79
00:04:43,819 --> 00:04:44,639
the outside world has spread rumors

80
00:04:44,939 --> 00:04:46,860
that you are a traitor

81
00:04:47,600 --> 00:04:49,800
who coerces the emperor to order the feudal lords.

82
00:04:50,519 --> 00:04:51,779
But no one knows

83
00:04:52,639 --> 00:04:55,199
that you have been teaching me governance day and night.

84
00:04:56,139 --> 00:04:58,040
In my heart, there is only respect,

85
00:04:58,839 --> 00:04:59,439
not fear.

86
00:05:01,600 --> 00:05:02,839
I won't read it again.

87
00:05:03,259 --> 00:05:03,740
Brother,

88
00:05:04,180 --> 00:05:04,920
what do you mean?

89
00:05:06,060 --> 00:05:06,740
In these four years,

90
00:05:08,860 --> 00:05:10,120
Your Majesty has worked tirelessly,

91
00:05:10,959 --> 00:05:12,680
becoming well-versed in state affairs.

92
00:05:13,620 --> 00:05:14,939
Now that the empire is at peace,

93
00:05:15,319 --> 00:05:16,319
the court is stable,

94
00:05:17,480 --> 00:05:18,699
and Your Majesty's wedding is imminent,

95
00:05:19,779 --> 00:05:21,000
my mission is complete.

96
00:05:24,639 --> 00:05:25,600
From now on,

97
00:05:27,220 --> 00:05:28,740
[I'll go to where I should go.]

98
00:05:52,459 --> 00:05:53,079
[Luo Yao,]

99
00:05:55,660 --> 00:05:57,560
[I've achieved the peace]

100
00:05:58,879 --> 00:05:59,639
[you sacrificed your life for.]

101
00:06:07,980 --> 00:06:09,379
[But the world without you]

102
00:06:14,180 --> 00:06:15,240
[is too cold.]

103
00:06:43,019 --> 00:06:43,959
[I'll come to you.]

104
00:07:19,139 --> 00:07:19,939
Xie Lingfeng,

105
00:07:20,860 --> 00:07:21,939
did I allow you to die?

106
00:07:33,060 --> 00:07:33,759
Luo Yao,

107
00:07:37,740 --> 00:07:38,779
Even if we can save the master,

108
00:07:39,399 --> 00:07:40,259
I'll lose half of my life.

109
00:07:41,180 --> 00:07:42,500
It's likely that only one of An Rao

110
00:07:43,160 --> 00:07:44,379
and the master can be saved.

111
00:07:49,639 --> 00:07:50,199
Sister,

112
00:07:51,040 --> 00:07:52,500
we finally meet.

113
00:08:02,160 --> 00:08:04,180
You've been through a lot.

114
00:08:09,360 --> 00:08:10,560
My journey is over.

115
00:08:14,980 --> 00:08:15,439
An Rao,

116
00:08:16,399 --> 00:08:16,939
from now on,

117
00:08:17,639 --> 00:08:18,560
you should keep going.

118
00:08:21,399 --> 00:08:22,040
In the past,

119
00:08:22,540 --> 00:08:23,959
you always protected me.

120
00:08:24,839 --> 00:08:25,540
Now,

121
00:08:26,620 --> 00:08:27,720
it's my turn to protect you.

122
00:08:31,240 --> 00:08:31,779
If it weren't

123
00:08:31,819 --> 00:08:33,100
for those changes,

124
00:08:37,240 --> 00:08:37,559
you would still

125
00:08:37,620 --> 00:08:39,019
be as pure as before.

126
00:08:39,639 --> 00:08:40,159
But I,

127
00:08:40,759 --> 00:08:41,759
with blood on my hands

128
00:08:42,539 --> 00:08:43,480
and revenge in my heart,

129
00:08:50,000 --> 00:08:51,100
There's no going back.

130
00:08:51,480 --> 00:08:52,539
But to me,

131
00:08:53,519 --> 00:08:54,480
you're always the one

132
00:08:54,659 --> 00:08:55,419
who pulled me out

133
00:08:55,539 --> 00:08:56,460
of the ruins.

134
00:08:57,519 --> 00:08:58,860
If you had no kindness in your heart,

135
00:08:59,779 --> 00:09:01,039
how could I have been born?

136
00:09:05,240 --> 00:09:06,460
I'm content

137
00:09:06,820 --> 00:09:07,960
just to have lived this life.

138
00:09:09,419 --> 00:09:09,960
So,

139
00:09:11,220 --> 00:09:12,279
let me do one last thing

140
00:09:13,340 --> 00:09:14,539
for you.

141
00:09:16,519 --> 00:09:17,019
No.

142
00:09:19,480 --> 00:09:19,960
An Rao.

143
00:09:21,320 --> 00:09:21,779
An Rao.

144
00:09:23,879 --> 00:09:24,360
No.

145
00:09:25,899 --> 00:09:26,580
Sister,

146
00:09:27,679 --> 00:09:30,259
there are people who care about you in this world.

147
00:09:31,159 --> 00:09:32,799
You must live well,

148
00:09:33,940 --> 00:09:35,519
including my name.

149
00:09:36,879 --> 00:09:37,539
An Rao.

150
00:09:42,019 --> 00:09:42,980
An Rao, I wish you

151
00:09:44,360 --> 00:09:45,779
a life of peace.

152
00:09:47,279 --> 00:09:47,960
And

153
00:09:49,220 --> 00:09:50,379
forgive yourself.

154
00:09:50,899 --> 00:09:51,360
Don't!

155
00:10:19,139 --> 00:10:19,940
Your life

156
00:10:22,320 --> 00:10:23,600
is mine to control!

157
00:10:25,840 --> 00:10:27,480
My life has been yours all along.

158
00:10:29,460 --> 00:10:30,799
But now, you are mine.
